content: Now that I have the contact info, I'll go ahead and cancel my Entertainment Weekly subscription. After that, I'll start sorting through my other magazines. I have a few indie magazines like Juxtapoz that I'm really enjoying, but I'm not sure about The New Yorker. I've been reading it regularly, but I'm starting to feel overwhelmed by the amount of content. Do you have any tips on how to stay on top of weekly magazines like that?
